{"tid":2378842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佐敦封區｜商戶損失慘重問有否補償 淒涼街坊乾哽公仔麵牙刷充筷子","createTime":"2021-01-24T21:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T06:27:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":73,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee13f5156064c2b433dd54f86e2bfed5811af19","tid":2378842,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T21:42:21.000Z","msg":"昨天因街坊來電要求曾一度開舖為他們服務，但其後有警察及工作人員前來阻止，「而家檢測緊，你要拉番度閘呀！有前來講物的街坊訴苦，啲街坊因沒有水煲，要乾哽公仔麵，有啲因為沒有筷子，要用牙刷代替進食，好淒涼！」<br />\n<br />\n黃小姐續表示，封區當日凌晨3時55分，「有警員及工作人員到來通知，說4時要關舖離開，個刻真係好嬲，我點走得切呀！之後，附近有餐廳東主問過幾個部門，問可否繼續營業，警察、市政.....等3個部門，有啲話得，有啲又話唔得，無所適從囉！商戶今次受影響無生意都要交舖租損失不少，政府會否有補償，啲高官真係好，個個月幾十萬人工，攞到成個床下底都係錢，點會理我哋個啲草根階層，我哋就搵一餐食一餐，佢係離地到不得了，我兩日已蝕約一萬元，相當頭痛。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210125/XQNGME2DTVAMDBODQCQSPM5XDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210125%2FXQNGME2DTVAMDBODQCQSPM5XDU%2F&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCIL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=8a054fa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210125%2FXQNGME2DTVAMDBODQCQSPM5XDU%2F&h=ce530ee3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210125/XQNGME2DTVAMDBODQCQSPM5XDU/</a>"},{"pid":"38dfde884f04e040688c0d985f6e5475d40f5455","tid":2378842,"uid":325346,"like":38,"dislike":10,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T21:49:10.000Z","msg":"有d人拎食物已經好開心"},{"pid":"7d4ef0a430639e61944383daab565610076746d1","tid":2378842,"uid":383344,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T21:50:03.000Z","msg":"前來講物"},{"pid":"6a1eb7c6a4fb9df6a4600f768771dfaeb558851d","tid":2378842,"uid":237425,"like":6,"dislike":38,"score":-32,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T22:43:32.000Z","msg":"佢係咪藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0a10d5e01f7e5aaf2f35c3fcfb38260ce309a9","tid":2378842,"uid":73473,"like":21,"d